.TH "pcim_iomap_regions" 9 "pcim_iomap_regions" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pcim_iomap_regions \- Request and iomap PCI BARs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pcim_iomap_regions
.BI "(struct pci_dev *pdev "  ","
.BI "int mask "  ","
.BI "const char *name "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pdev" 12
PCI device to map IO resources for
.IP "mask" 12
Mask of BARs to request and iomap
.IP "name" 12
Name used when requesting regions
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Request and iomap regions specified by \fImask\fP.
